{"title":"报到流程","icon":"flow","shareable":true,"id":"newcomer/check/after-flow","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"后续报到流程"},{"tag":"text","text":["在食堂的自助终端机处修改密码与消费限额"],"align":"center"},{"tag":"text","text":["👇"],"align":"center","style":"font-weight:500;font-size:20px;"},{"tag":"text","text":["上楼并简单整理行李，之后提前完成下列工作","通过微信企业号或支付宝提前对校园卡完成充值","可通过微信企业号校园卡栏目提前缴纳网费","到洗漱间和热水间检查是否可以刷出生活用水和饮用水 (生活用水白天不供应，但是应该会显示升数，不能使用会显示错误码)"],"align":"center"},{"tag":"text","text":["👇"],"align":"center","style":"font-weight:500;font-size:20px;"},{"tag":"text","text":["按照小程序需带物品章节对自身携带物品进行核对，并列出购物清单前往学校超市进行购买"],"align":"center"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"需带物品","icon":"necessity","path":"newcomer/necessity/index"}]},{"tag":"text","text":["👇"],"align":"center","style":"font-weight:500;font-size:20px;"},{"tag":"text","text":["到校园快递中心 (本部菜鸟驿站、净月菜鸟驿站) 取快递"],"align":"center"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"快递","icon":"express","path":"guide/express/index"}]},{"tag":"text","text":["👇"],"align":"center","style":"font-weight:500;font-size:20px;"},{"tag":"text","text":["根据自身需求按需去浴池洗浴，晚上按时归寝等待导员查寝"],"align":"center"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"校园浴池","icon":"bath","path":"guide/bath/index"}]}],"time":"2023 年 9 月 23 日 12:11:49"}